			<para>WiFi Protected Access (WPA)基于WEP，且更加安全。</para>
			<para>WPA在<application>Network Manager</application>集成了。你还需要安装<application>wpasupplicant</application>。</para>
			<para>如果你需要手动配置WPA支持，请参阅<ulink url="https://help.ubuntu.com/community/WifiDocs/WPAHowTo?highlight=%28wpa%29">Wiki Entry</ulink>。</para>
